https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/j6VDPhntesW1D1cS5nRcYZp7DAj.jpg After witnessing their parents murder as infants, June and Carl have held a deadly secret throughout their entire lives, a secret that none will believe. Years later, June is back to investigate the family home after her estranged brother Carl's mysterious suicide. As she walks the grounds, and inhabits the house, June learns that the Scarecrow who came to take her family is walking once again and is seeking revenge on the town. Curse of the Scarecrow
